The paper discusses a security vulnerability in video surveillance systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on the use of motion detection and object detection in smart video surveillance systems, which relates to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The proposed detection technique using electrical network frequency (ENF) reference database falls under signal processing (cs.SI) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
